bodyEn:
1. IMPS charge of Rs. {AMOUNT} was levied on {TXN_DATE} (UTR {UTR}) by {BANK_NAME}. As per RBI's digital-payment directive, IMPS via digital channel is free for amounts up to Rs. 1,000 and capped thereafter. Reverse the excess.

Attachments: bank statement, sanction letter, RBI Master Circular reference.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
